   Thursday's Markets:
   Stocks Slide
   As Oil Prices
   Rise Sharply
   ---
   Expectation of Cuts
   In Earnings Estimates
   Drives Down Shares
   ----
   By Christopher Winans
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
